<br />
<br />P.S.: Did you note that, although the game was made in the 80s where women were rather bushy, they already foresaw today's trend of women shaving "down there". I mean, the foundation of the Galactic Federation takes place in 2000 and "Metroid" takes place in 20X5. So, if 20X5 is 2005 or 2015 or if this trend doesn't change in the next decades, they did a really good job with their prediction.

		

